    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "## theInterview (PICT)"
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0248",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "Web app for sharing and discovering interview/placement experiences (PICT community). Built with **Next.js App Router**, **NextAuth (Google)**, and **MongoDB**."
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0249",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "## Getting started (local development)"
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0250",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "```bash npm install npm run dev ```"
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0251",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "Then open `http://localhost:3000`."
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0252",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "### Environment variables"
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0253",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "Create a `.env.local` at the project root:"
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0254",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "```bash # MongoDB MONGODB_URI=\"mongodb+srv://...\""
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0255",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "# NextAuth (Google) GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=\"...\" GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=\"...\""
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0256",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "# Recommended (NextAuth) NEXTAUTH_URL=\"http://localhost:3000\" NEXTAUTH_SECRET=\"replace-with-a-long-random-secret\""
  },
  {
    "id": "chunk_0257",
    "type": "content-text",
    "source": "README.md",
    "content": "# Email (used by /api/saveExp and /api/sendEmail) EMAIL_USER=\"yourgmail@gmail.com\" EMAIL_PASS=\"gmail-app-password\" ```"
  },
